  array('id_index'=>7683,'id'=>214459,'name'=>'Six Flags','description'=>'For almost fifty years the name \"Six Flags\" has been synonymous with fun.  Founded in 1961, Six Flags began with Six Flags Over Texas - named for the fact that six flags (Spain, France, Mexico, Republic of Texas, Confederate and U.S.) have been flown in the state of Texas during its history.  Despite the multi-cultural origin of its name, Six Flags is a uniquely American experience.  With 21 locations in North America - including Six Flags Magic Mountain, Six Flags America and Six Flags Great Adventure - Six Flags is one of the world\'s largest theme-park chains with approximately 25 million visitors each year.  

